---
const articles = [
  { slug: 'the-five-pillars', title: 'The Five Pillars: how we score an estate' },
  { slug: 'uk-data-residency-enforced', title: "Why “UK data residency” is meaningless unless it's enforced" },
  { slug: 'the-technical-debt-burden', title: 'The Technical Debt Burden: putting a £ figure on legacy IT' },
];
---
<section class="credibility section">
  <div class="container">
    <h2 class="credibility__headline text-column" data-fade>Built in the open.</h2>
    <p class="credibility__body text-column" data-fade style="--fade-delay:80ms">
      The existing market produced the problem. We are not going to solve it by operating
      the same way. We publish the methodology behind the Sovereignty Index™, the
      architecture principles behind the Sovereign Vault, and our thinking as it develops —
      because a firm worth trusting with your infrastructure should be able to show its
      working. We will not offer you invented client logos or anonymous testimonials.
      Judge us on the work.
    </p>

    <ul class="credibility__list">
      {articles.map((article, i) => (
        <li data-fade style={`--fade-delay:${160 + i * 80}ms`}>
          <a href={`/insights/${article.slug}/`} class="credibility__link">
            <span>{article.title}</span>
            <span class="credibility__arrow" aria-hidden="true">→</span>
          </a>
        </li>
      ))}
    </ul>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .credibility__headline {
    font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 4vw, 2.6rem);
  }

  .credibility__body {
    margin-top: var(--space-md);
    color: var(--colour-text-muted);
    font-size: 1.05rem;
  }

  .credibility__list {
    margin-top: var(--space-xl);
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--colour-hairline);
  }

  .credibility__link {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: var(--space-md);
    padding: var(--space-md) 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--colour-hairline);
    text-decoration: none;
    color: var(--colour-text);
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    transition: color 220ms var(--ease-quiet), padding-left 220ms var(--ease-quiet);
  }

  .credibility__link:hover,
  .credibility__link:focus-visible {
    color: var(--colour-accent);
    padding-left: 0.4rem;
  }

  .credibility__arrow {
    color: var(--colour-text-muted);
    transition: transform 220ms var(--ease-quiet);
  }

  .credibility__link:hover .credibility__arrow {
    transform: translateX(4px);
  }
</style>
